      "updated": 1775268712895,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "why CPU don't store value in itself?\"\n\"CPU सानो हुन्छ र धेरै डाटा अटाउँदैन\"\n CPU भित्र एउटा सानो मेमोरी हुन्छ जसलाई Registers भनिन्छ। \n\"CPU has very small storage called Registers for immediate calculation\"",
      "fontSize": 15.445931107334898,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "why CPU don't store value in itself?\"\n\"CPU सानो हुन्छ र धेरै डाटा अटाउँदैन\"\n CPU भित्र एउटा सानो मेमोरी हुन्छ जसलाई Registers भनिन्छ। \n\"CPU has very small storage called Registers for immediate calculation\"",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
