      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775531925901,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "२. Address Generation (The 2n Rule):\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "२. Address Generation (The 2n Rule):\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Y-O7yxvF_ZGvYyOiJw8Xu",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 837.7003220670015,
      "y": 1252.9677944820876,
      "width": 715.1114666234411,
      "height": 61.97956428870933,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "cF50sMR7rUhrPY_7MHJax",
        "WX5493mj9W5moNtPQnKbx",
        "R6ml28NsZNZI6-EkqoU8D",
        "LLjSiyTEx9mJ5Jvz8Zeg4"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b74",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1418384237,
      "version": 933,
      "versionNonce": 1201892247,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775531925901,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "16-Byte RAM: यदि १६-बाइटको र्‍याम छ भने, १६ वटा ब्लक हुन्छन् र ती सबैलाई १६ वटा युनिक एड्रेस चाहिन्छ। \n    यसका लागि 4-bit (24=16) भए पुग्छ। Example: 0000 देखि 1111 सम्मका ठेगानाहरू।\n",
      "fontSize": 16.52788381032249,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "16-Byte RAM: यदि १६-बाइटको र्‍याम छ भने, १६ वटा ब्लक हुन्छन् र ती सबैलाई १६ वटा युनिक एड्रेस चाहिन्छ। \n    यसका लागि 4-bit (24=16) भए पुग्छ। Example: 0000 देखि 1111 सम्मका ठेगानाहरू।\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "QGeytWOehE7bt5T56oQB1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 840.4936394199046,
      "y": 1229.6555094719902,
      "width": 517.4380166032629,
      "height": 41.31970952580622,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
