      "versionNonce": 122420569,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775531925901,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "मेमोरीको साइज अनुसार कति 'Bit' को एड्रेस चाहिन्छ भन्ने कुरा यसरी हिसाब गरिन्छ:\n",
      "fontSize": 16.52788381032249,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "मेमोरीको साइज अनुसार कति 'Bit' को एड्रेस चाहिन्छ भन्ने कुरा यसरी हिसाब गरिन्छ:\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "MhFV38njNdPc9Qp23HIia",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 810.37615404337,
      "y": 1301.151585999517,
      "width": 717.1773512215342,
      "height": 61.97956428870933,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#6741d9",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "cF50sMR7rUhrPY_7MHJax",
        "WX5493mj9W5moNtPQnKbx",
        "R6ml28NsZNZI6-EkqoU8D",
        "LLjSiyTEx9mJ5Jvz8Zeg4"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b76",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 893045293,
      "version": 1037,
      "versionNonce": 1635770551,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775531925901,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "    32-Byte RAM: यदि ३२-बाइटको र्‍याम छ भने, ३२ वटा ब्लक र ३२ वटा एड्रेस चाहिन्छ। यसका लागि 5-bit \n        (25=32) आवश्यक पर्छ।\n",
      "fontSize": 16.527883810322486,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "    32-Byte RAM: यदि ३२-बाइटको र्‍याम छ भने, ३२ वटा ब्लक र ३२ वटा एड्रेस चाहिन्छ। यसका लागि 5-bit \n        (25=32) आवश्यक पर्छ।\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "t3c-8W4VJCKWbFyTrKXz2",
