      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775281499863,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "१. समस्या: No Continuous Space (मेमोरीको अभाव)\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "१. समस्या: No Continuous Space (मेमोरीको अभाव)\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "1Bac418M0Bdi4aiquau87",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 469.04964619357565,
      "y": 3162.964775832832,
      "width": 709.920166015625,
      "height": 41.122260264677834,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#9c36b5",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "rN3Urbj6OU3Q6TGkjl3OU"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b7A",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 253690381,
      "version": 240,
      "versionNonce": 1807948459,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775359688290,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "स्ट्याकमा डाटाहरू एकपछि अर्को गरी टम्म मिलेर बसेका हुन्छन्। यदि हामीले b (एड्रेस 0001) लाई अपडेट गरेर \n३-बाइटको बनाउन खोज्यौँ भने, त्यहाँ थपिने ठाउँ हुँदैन। किनकि त्यसको लगत्तै मुनि अर्को भ्यारिएबल बसिसकेको हुन्छ।",
      "fontSize": 16.448904105871133,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "स्ट्याकमा डाटाहरू एकपछि अर्को गरी टम्म मिलेर बसेका हुन्छन्। यदि हामीले b (एड्रेस 0001) लाई अपडेट गरेर \n३-बाइटको बनाउन खोज्यौँ भने, त्यहाँ थपिने ठाउँ हुँदैन। किनकि त्यसको लगत्तै मुनि अर्को भ्यारिएबल बसिसकेको हुन्छ।",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Hr5tU45lm2BwiTnKMouwn",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 436.49766455245253,
      "y": 3217.5039969200825,
      "width": 438.2396240234375,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "rN3Urbj6OU3Q6TGkjl3OU"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
