      "seed": 1779521795,
      "version": 170,
      "versionNonce": 1263905027,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775281499863,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "२. समाधान र त्यसको मूल्य (The Cost of Shifting):\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "२. समाधान र त्यसको मूल्य (The Cost of Shifting):\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "IDVgGrciobibPotUfKK-D",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 510.23621173165066,
      "y": 3248.299124622118,
      "width": 432.1878662109375,
      "height": 42.159875300895266,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "rN3Urbj6OU3Q6TGkjl3OU"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b7C",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1295153485,
      "version": 196,
      "versionNonce": 627019939,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775281499863,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "यो अपडेट गर्न हामीसँग दुईवटा विकल्प हुन्छन्, तर दुवै झन्झटिला छन्:\n",
      "fontSize": 16.863950120358105,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "यो अपडेट गर्न हामीसँग दुईवटा विकल्प हुन्छन्, तर दुवै झन्झटिला छन्:\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "uJ6deCFPwINamqOSxvY1I",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 478.2091449424197,
      "y": 3276.60606581968,
      "width": 732.5098502288516,
      "height": 39.62580448722981,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#0c8599",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "rN3Urbj6OU3Q6TGkjl3OU"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b7D",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 718362253,
      "version": 335,
      "versionNonce": 1628144707,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775281499863,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "    Option A: यो अपडेटेड भ्यालुलाई स्ट्याकको सबैभन्दा माथि (Top) नयाँ लोकेसनमा राख्ने र पुरानो एड्रेस Delete गर्ने।\n",
      "fontSize": 15.850321794891926,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "    Option A: यो अपडेटेड भ्यालुलाई स्ट्याकको सबैभन्दा माथि (Top) नयाँ लोकेसनमा राख्ने र पुरानो एड्रेस Delete गर्ने।\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
