      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "testai object ko sath ma ni yestai hunxa ,jaha space milxa tehi store gardax , sni object update vax vane same location lai \nmanipulate garna khojxa , contineous memory navettayama khali memory find gari updated object ref stack ma store gardax.\nani ti de-reference heap memory location (object, '0x55a') haru GC le clean gardax.",
