      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775540894137,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "aba hamro program kahi pani '0' use garnu x vane array ko '1000' location point garaune. ra loop ma pani i le yahi array ko element point gari loop \ni ko value tarantar create nagarne. yasari easy solution vayo. tara problem chai 1lakh size ko array banaunu ma hunxa, 1element le 8 byte lida\n1lakh element le 8lakh byte memory ta array le matra fixed line vayo heap ma.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "aba hamro program kahi pani '0' use garnu x vane array ko '1000' location point garaune. ra loop ma pani i le yahi array ko element point gari loop \ni ko value tarantar create nagarne. yasari easy solution vayo. tara problem chai 1lakh size ko array banaunu ma hunxa, 1element le 8 byte lida\n1lakh element le 8lakh byte memory ta array le matra fixed line vayo heap ma.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
