      "updated": 1775542201141,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "aba 1-bit tag ko rup ma use garec baki basyo 31 bit jaha 2 ^ 31 address hunxa ra highest value\n2 ^ 31 - 1 positive value if unsigned ho vane ,tara signed system ma yo 2^30 lai ni aadhi garinxa\nfor negative ra positive value. kina 2^30 vanda one bit for signed value hunxa ni ta feri. ra yo +( 2^30)- 1 dekhi -(2^30) \nsammko range lai smi(Small Integer) maninx ra yo range ma naaaune number ra floating point number \nharu lai heap mai store gardaxa.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "aba 1-bit tag ko rup ma use garec baki basyo 31 bit jaha 2 ^ 31 address hunxa ra highest value\n2 ^ 31 - 1 positive value if unsigned ho vane ,tara signed system ma yo 2^30 lai ni aadhi garinxa\nfor negative ra positive value. kina 2^30 vanda one bit for signed value hunxa ni ta feri. ra yo +( 2^30)- 1 dekhi -(2^30) \nsammko range lai smi(Small Integer) maninx ra yo range ma naaaune number ra floating point number \nharu lai heap mai store gardaxa.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
